## What We're Building

**VoiceOS** — A multi-tenant SaaS platform where any business (clinic, hotel, e-com store) gets a custom AI voice agent on their phone number in under 10 minutes. Self-serve onboarding + agency white-label.

Not "another chatbot." The positioning: **"Your AI receptionist that actually works — answers every call, books appointments, resolves tickets, never sleeps."**

