## Architecture (Powered by Supabase + ElevenLabs)

```text
VoiceOS Platform
├── Super Admin (you)
│   ├── All tenants overview
│   ├── Usage, billing metrics & revenue dashboard
│   └── Global agent template management
│
├── Tenant Dashboard (each business)
│   ├── Onboarding wizard (vertical picker, business info, phone setup)
│   ├── Agent Studio (prompt, voice, language, fallback behavior)
│   ├── Integrations Hub (Google Calendar, Shopify, Zendesk, Make/Zapier)
│   ├── Call Logs (transcripts + cached audio via Supabase Storage)
│   └── Real-time Analytics (live dashboards powered by Supabase Realtime)
│
└── Voice Agent Pipeline (per tenant)
    ├── ElevenLabs agent (auto-provisioned via secure API)
    ├── Twilio routing (incoming calls map to tenant ID automatically)
    └── Serverless Tools (Calendar booking, order lookup, ticket creation)
```

