## Database Schema (Supabase PostgreSQL)
*Protected by strong Row-Level Security (RLS) guaranteeing absolute tenant isolation.*

```text
profiles          — id, name, email, role (super_admin/tenant_admin), tenant_id
tenants           — id, name, vertical, slug, plan, agent config details
integrations      — tenant_id, type (google_calendar/shopify/zendesk), encrypted credentials
call_logs         — id, tenant_id, caller, duration, outcome, transcript, conversation_id
bookings          — id, tenant_id, caller details, slot_start, slot_end, google_event_id
demo_orders       — id, tenant_id, order details, total, delivery status
```

